{"tid":189172,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[JR Pass + USJ] 大阪行程求教","createTime":"2017-04-06T08:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:54:15.000Z","uid":103946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c60db6e8bdbc58f4ac7c9573339e41c5339c426","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，小弟打算嚟緊五月去大阪，行程暫時咁樣plan:<br />\n<br />\nDay 0: 香港 &rarr; 大阪 &rarr; 天王寺 <br />\nDay 1: 環球影城<br />\nDay 2: 祇園、八阪神社、京都文化博物館、京都國際漫畫博物館<br />\nDay 3: 京都塔、京都鐵道博物館、京都國立博物館<br />\nDay 4: 姬路城<br />\nDay 5: 大阪城 &rarr; 關西機場 &rarr; 香港<br />\n<br />\n住宿方面就咁樣安排:<br />\nDay 0, day 1晚 book左天王寺附近酒店<br />\nDay 2, day 3 晚 book左京都站附近酒店<br />\n至於Day 4晚就 book左難波附近酒店<br />\n<br />\n想請教下各位，呢個行程適唔適合買JR pass? 我粗略估算呢6日大概要用10000 yen搭車 ，買JR pass好似會平少少。但上網check過，最合適果張(關西廣域鐵路周遊券)好似淨係包5日，會唔會唔抵? 或者有無其他更好選擇?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_wide/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_wide%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=dd712227\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai_wide/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外去環球影城想問下一個人去駛唔駛買埋express pass? 我係5月嘅平日去嘅，一個人排會唔會排得快D? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9805baa39f112b89f6dc3fd6da59b133d755b9","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f873abf0e527ea9eeccaa2f0f14496aaa733de13","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9xmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9xmg.jpg&h=1b3c5208&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83f5d1903b40edad5cb1d6521342b02cbecf1b2c","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702b3ba1afe408f691e8e07186c902ec01b0c5df","tid":189172,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"唔好分咁散住 幾麻煩"},{"pid":"9a39b6580cc4578efa1f5fc8eeafa49cf104a643","tid":189172,"uid":6032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"奈良 唔去？"},{"pid":"615843c22a41a9c825a6392f42be6165f2fd8a0c","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好分咁散住 幾麻煩</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbook酒店果陣諗住中間\u0010兩日可以浸下溫泉<br />\n同埋京都大阪來回差唔多兩個鐘<br />\n宜家一諗好似真係有D麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34f08e6ab5ace0883e5c42f8a7ddcbe7ffbf6f5","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奈良 唔去？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對睇鹿唔係好大興趣<br />\n想睇城同博物館多D"},{"pid":"c09e5b33c99a7b540d02708da42c65c32bd4bc24","tid":189172,"uid":53041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"去同返 係幾點鐘機??"},{"pid":"1d1bd7f05f4137f6e57ace89a3ff89a75e3fd389","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去同返 係幾點鐘機??</blockquote><br />\n去程16:10到關西機場<br />\n回程17:40關西機場起飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee9fd09b41c374587520b1998682f59fbbcb727","tid":189172,"uid":28697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e756008812fda9db7cc968bbc89cea7b6a9d077f","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問IC card外國人版係咪要響香港買定先? 定係大阪果邊機場買?<br />\nUSJ排100分鐘真係好誇張，咁應該都會買pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5a359c2b1a7ac4686f3b1c58c565c9b5a1eb4d","tid":189172,"uid":28697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問IC card外國人版係咪要響香港買定先? 定係大阪果邊機場買?<br />\nUSJ排100分鐘真係好誇張，咁應該都會買pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我喺機揚外面果個鐵路站買既，2000yen, 500 yen係卡既鐵，1500yen就係您撘幾多扣幾多，原理同八達通一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外國人IC card係有隻阿童木喺上面架:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/200733_695df5ee24492ac6cb6dbfd57dc0ac4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F200733_695df5ee24492ac6cb6dbfd57dc0ac4b.jpg&h=a538a501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nExpress分幾種架，你可以選擇您想玩既再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要喺香港買左先，熱門好快爆！"},{"pid":"c4c9521c02780509edec5f45ec7628356eb61748","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問IC card外國人版係咪要響香港買定先? 定係大阪果邊機場買?<br />\nUSJ排100分鐘真係好誇張，咁應該都會買pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我喺機揚外面果個鐵路站買既，2000yen, 500 yen係卡既鐵，1500yen就係您撘幾多扣幾多，原理同八達通一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外國人IC card係有隻阿童木喺上面架:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/200733_695df5ee24492ac6cb6dbfd57dc0ac4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F200733_695df5ee24492ac6cb6dbfd57dc0ac4b.jpg&h=a538a501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nExpress分幾種架，你可以選擇您想玩既再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要喺香港買左先，熱門好快爆！</blockquote><br />\n明白，唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73958a0caa054fab43d97969115ef16a7d68983","tid":189172,"uid":58675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIC卡同西瓜卡有無分別？<br />\n因為當年去東京買左西瓜卡<br />\n可否在大阪用？Thanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b4be78cba257b88951a5ac339b6960828e3320","tid":189172,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIC卡同西瓜卡有無分別？<br />\n因為當年去東京買左西瓜卡<br />\n可否在大阪用？Thanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuica, pasmo, icoca等等, 統稱IC卡<br />\n大部分都已經共通"},{"pid":"fef79b6dc65eb7194f2619908c54ee82c4eb0cfe","tid":189172,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴絲，小弟打算嚟緊五月去大阪，行程暫時咁樣plan:<br />\n<br />\nDay 0: 香港 &rarr; 大阪 &rarr; 天王寺 <br />\nDay 1: 環球影城<br />\nDay 2: 祇園、八阪神社、京都文化博物館、京都國際漫畫博物館<br />\nDay 3: 京都塔、京都鐵道博物館、京都國立博物館<br />\nDay 4: 姬路城<br />\nDay 5: 大阪城 &rarr; 關西機場 &rarr; 香港<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n來回機場買haruka來回票<br />\n去USJ車費好平<br />\n京都市內搭巴士一日500YEN任搭<br />\n淨係Day 4買一日JR Pass就夠"},{"pid":"23252ecc7ba81cc950d9c71b108a1c7bef1a4b44","tid":189172,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>各位巴絲，小弟打算嚟緊五月去大阪，行程暫時咁樣plan:<br />\n<br />\nDay 0: 香港 &rarr; 大阪 &rarr; 天王寺 <br />\nDay 1: 環球影城<br />\nDay 2: 祇園、八阪神社、京都文化博物館、京都國際漫畫博物館<br />\nDay 3: 京都塔、京都鐵道博物館、京都國立博物館<br />\nDay 4: 姬路城<br />\nDay 5: 大阪城 &rarr; 關西機場 &rarr; 香港<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n來回機場買haruka來回票<br />\n去USJ車費好平<br />\n京都市內搭巴士一日500YEN任搭<br />\n淨係Day 4買一日JR Pass就夠</blockquote><br />\n頭先上網search<br />\n原來haruka可以連IC買<br />\n多謝巴打提議"},{"pid":"e3d61839c5fb9ae74efd2281d37e546ec114f0eb","tid":189172,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"Day 3不如調轉次序，京都塔放最後"},{"pid":"2703f5ac0eab8f51dfa547d493541dd633b50bfb","tid":189172,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"記住 USJ要買 fast pass!!"},{"pid":"812d281220001702db78d211386e32808eb3006f","tid":189172,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:43:58.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得六日都住大阪同一間酒店比較好 唔使將啲野搬來搬去<br />\n不過你都book哂 咁冇計了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3464038d8a315005c55ec4a310e8a0faf51523f","tid":189172,"uid":16261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"搭單問有冇人玩左DQ? 好唔好玩?"},{"pid":"a66d221c43970ec664c4d2df8ea79d13f3f3c5b6","tid":189172,"uid":92806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"巴打你好，我一月個時去大阪同你嘅行程plan類似，不過我無去到姬路而係去左奈良同神户。因為你去嘅地方唔多，我唔太建議買關西周遊卡或者jp pass，同樓上絲打講法一樣，用ic card已經足夠。京都行程放最前，之後大阪，最多住兩間酒店就好，另外我覺得大阪嘅airbnb都唔差，不如住民宿。我都有去到usj，三個人去無買express，排隊仲耐過訓覺，同埋好少game有single，所以都係唔好慳錢。我usj飛上klook買會平過上官網訂，中意可以search下。"},{"pid":"7958759667a49361ace4206537c8a9fb15f197cd","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先上網search<br />\n原來haruka可以連IC買<br />\n多謝巴打提議</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似咁買抵D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\nDay 3不如調轉次序，京都塔放最後<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n除左頭尾兩日，其他幾日仲未排好次序，京都塔應該會放夜晚<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n巴打你好，我一月個時去大阪同你嘅行程plan類似，不過我無去到姬路而係去左奈良同神户。因為你去嘅地方唔多，我唔太建議買關西周遊卡或者jp pass，同樓上絲打講法一樣，用ic card已經足夠。京都行程放最前，之後大阪，最多住兩間酒店就好，另外我覺得大阪嘅airbnb都唔差，不如住民宿。我都有去到usj，三個人去無買express，排隊仲耐過訓覺，同埋好少game有single，所以都係唔好慳錢。我usj飛上klook買會平過上官網訂，中意可以search下。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n絲打你好，我對airbnb 有陰影，上年同另外3個朋友去東京住airbnb，住之前個host聲稱單位可以住5個人。點知去到個單位得一個廳，打地鋪訓3個已經唔夠位，我就訓走廊。D被鋪仲要好似無洗過咁，已經唔敢再住airbnb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f243ad6a82c0e2e152b52ea5dcd5c2383050c778","tid":189172,"uid":6032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奈良 唔去？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對睇鹿唔係好大興趣<br />\n想睇城同博物館多D</blockquote><br />\n奈良都好多博物館睇"},{"pid":"4a42d424a0c496e98f33ccef9fcbf0d88daf8564","tid":189172,"uid":49546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"有無人講下usj入面點玩<br />\n除左第一樣玩哈利波特之外<br />\n仲有咩必玩同玩先<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091cb17b5d9646128d450bddc15f619b9ce23ab3","tid":189172,"uid":92806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭先上網search<br />\n原來haruka可以連IC買<br />\n多謝巴打提議</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似咁買抵D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\nDay 3不如調轉次序，京都塔放最後<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n除左頭尾兩日，其他幾日仲未排好次序，京都塔應該會放夜晚<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n巴打你好，我一月個時去大阪同你嘅行程plan類似，不過我無去到姬路而係去左奈良同神户。因為你去嘅地方唔多，我唔太建議買關西周遊卡或者jp pass，同樓上絲打講法一樣，用ic card已經足夠。京都行程放最前，之後大阪，最多住兩間酒店就好，另外我覺得大阪嘅airbnb都唔差，不如住民宿。我都有去到usj，三個人去無買express，排隊仲耐過訓覺，同埋好少game有single，所以都係唔好慳錢。我usj飛上klook買會平過上官網訂，中意可以search下。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n絲打你好，我對airbnb 有陰影，上年同另外3個朋友去東京住airbnb，住之前個host聲稱單位可以住5個人。點知去到個單位得一個廳，打地鋪訓3個已經唔夠位，我就訓走廊。D被鋪仲要好似無洗過咁，已經唔敢再住airbnb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 原來係咁，但你酒店個價貴唔貴？<br />\n同埋見巴打你編嘅行程，係唔係一支公去同埋自己本身中意睇名勝古蹟多於食野行街？"},{"pid":"c52f23b84949e200c13dfa60282bbcac3946e7b7","tid":189172,"uid":92806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人講下usj入面點玩<br />\n除左第一樣玩哈利波特之外<br />\n仲有咩必玩同玩先<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩先真心係哈利波特個個，不過千其唔好排錯隊，我上次勁on9咁一入去哈利波特城區見隊就排，排左成45分鐘以為有得玩，點知係派左個三枝魔杖嘅表演，再行去排個game個時已經排出去門口外仲要等兩個鐘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我玩過覺得spiderman都係值得一試。（飛天翼龍因為同行朋友唔敢玩，所以無玩到，但如果巴打中意過山車就認真必試）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdfbe3f786fda8b9c8819069ca7bb785bf995d3","tid":189172,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人講下usj入面點玩<br />\n除左第一樣玩哈利波特之外<br />\n仲有咩必玩同玩先<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛天翼龍 spiderman hollywood harry potter"},{"pid":"0bc651c48dc3ce11cb1623ec338f9ebb99a37dfb","tid":189172,"uid":7505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"你一個人去定同fd去呀?<br />\n我5月都去大阪wor"},{"pid":"bee6e1d6e0a78c9dab61cda8e63d29268917f67d","tid":189172,"uid":53041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"14/5 - 18/5  一個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba9cbcb0f40a873178972c5ee928144c275ad26","tid":189172,"uid":33740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"上次陪frd 7日去左4晚心齋橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fd7c8c5df891009a3f78c7a9950bd72f884b7a","tid":189172,"uid":28697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭先上網search<br />\n原來haruka可以連IC買<br />\n多謝巴打提議</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似咁買抵D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\nDay 3不如調轉次序，京都塔放最後<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n除左頭尾兩日，其他幾日仲未排好次序，京都塔應該會放夜晚<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n巴打你好，我一月個時去大阪同你嘅行程plan類似，不過我無去到姬路而係去左奈良同神户。因為你去嘅地方唔多，我唔太建議買關西周遊卡或者jp pass，同樓上絲打講法一樣，用ic card已經足夠。京都行程放最前，之後大阪，最多住兩間酒店就好，另外我覺得大阪嘅airbnb都唔差，不如住民宿。我都有去到usj，三個人去無買express，排隊仲耐過訓覺，同埋好少game有single，所以都係唔好慳錢。我usj飛上klook買會平過上官網訂，中意可以search下。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n絲打你好，我對airbnb 有陰影，上年同另外3個朋友去東京住airbnb，住之前個host聲稱單位可以住5個人。點知去到個單位得一個廳，打地鋪訓3個已經唔夠位，我就訓走廊。D被鋪仲要好似無洗過咁，已經唔敢再住airbnb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我住果間好正，500蚊左右晚，地點都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣可以介紹比您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be96b6b9025bdf0b48420580a3adadda4ed6a84","tid":189172,"uid":28697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人講下usj入面點玩<br />\n除左第一樣玩哈利波特之外<br />\n仲有咩必玩同玩先<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛天翼龍 spiderman hollywood harry potter</blockquote><br />\n如果係動漫迷就應該選擇去玩cool japan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77090bbabde1b08c235a3b6cfd0fc9875a2a4638","tid":189172,"uid":76166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"5月幾去？ 我5月尾都自己去 咩都未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46217d4898c3ff8fdba18e06ecb2b5b3b6e035c","tid":189172,"uid":45471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:13:39.000Z","msg":"你可以上網計下交通費佑唔值回張pass，定一係買關西周遊pass抵。<br />\n<br />\n一張三日卡都係2000yen(好似係)，但pass成15000yen。話唔定周遊卡加額外車費平pass成倍。<br />\n<br />\n利申係關西租獨立屋，大部分都係用周遊卡"},{"pid":"afdf07ad8a7a707af38b4401c652986544381a18","tid":189172,"uid":45471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問IC card外國人版係咪要響香港買定先? 定係大阪果邊機場買?<br />\nUSJ排100分鐘真係好誇張，咁應該都會買pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我喺機揚外面果個鐵路站買既，2000yen, 500 yen係卡既鐵，1500yen就係您撘幾多扣幾多，原理同八達通一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外國人IC card係有隻阿童木喺上面架:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/06/200733_695df5ee24492ac6cb6dbfd57dc0ac4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F200733_695df5ee24492ac6cb6dbfd57dc0ac4b.jpg&h=a538a501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nExpress分幾種架，你可以選擇您想玩既再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要喺香港買左先，熱門好快爆！</blockquote><br />\n明白，唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIC卡唔抵，你搭一程都成幾百yen，如果用翻原價去玩關西肯定好貴"},{"pid":"bd8eb236c680e5da516adcd54cf5866bebc49d3c","tid":189172,"uid":15005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T21:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人講下usj入面點玩<br />\n除左第一樣玩哈利波特之外<br />\n仲有咩必玩同玩先<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUsj揀好express種類同內容，其餘想玩、express冇包而一定要排好耐嘅（翼龍、逆轉世界、hp、eva)就開門跑過去。<br />\n<br />\n去前睇好地圖，mark好大概次序，唔好東西來回跑。<br />\n另外mark埋想睇嘅show嘅場次，等自己有得走盞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鍾意侏羅紀嘅睇恐龍個show包冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有環球影城巡遊我覺得一定要睇！氣氛超好，嗰種演員同遊客嘅互動到依家都仲回味緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我前排去完，次旺日。官方開園時間0830，我0610左右到大門，0730正式入園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣玩咗翼龍（超爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇諗過咁激）、MH(浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，終於明點解啲人玩完個樣好似唔知啱啱發生咗咩事咁）、Spiderman（好玩不過玩完呢個先玩禁忌之旅會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）、哥斯拉（冇乜特別）、大白鯊（玩過一次見識過就好）、侏羅紀乘船（會濕撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）、禁忌之旅（唔玩會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），其他時間用晒嚟影相、食嘢。<br />\n<br />\n翼龍一開門就跑去都要排30分鐘，出嚟已經去到200分鐘<br />\n買咗express4 :<br />\nSpiderman wait time 90分鐘，排5分鐘左右<br />\n侏羅紀、大白鯊冇留意wait time，排5-10分鐘<br />\n禁忌之旅wait time200分鐘，直入"},{"pid":"53de395d727d3165dd84ade14d8bfc2a597e6b39","tid":189172,"uid":58675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人講下usj入面點玩<br />\n除左第一樣玩哈利波特之外<br />\n仲有咩必玩同玩先<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUsj揀好express種類同內容，其餘想玩、express冇包而一定要排好耐嘅（翼龍、逆轉世界、hp、eva)就開門跑過去。<br />\n<br />\n去前睇好地圖，mark好大概次序，唔好東西來回跑。<br />\n另外mark埋想睇嘅show嘅場次，等自己有得走盞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鍾意侏羅紀嘅睇恐龍個show包冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有環球影城巡遊我覺得一定要睇！氣氛超好，嗰種演員同遊客嘅互動到依家都仲回味緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我前排去完，次旺日。官方開園時間0830，我0610左右到大門，0730正式入園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣玩咗翼龍（超爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇諗過咁激）、MH(浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，終於明點解啲人玩完個樣好似唔知啱啱發生咗咩事咁）、Spiderman（好玩不過玩完呢個先玩禁忌之旅會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）、哥斯拉（冇乜特別）、大白鯊（玩過一次見識過就好）、侏羅紀乘船（會濕撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）、禁忌之旅（唔玩會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），其他時間用晒嚟影相、食嘢。<br />\n<br />\n翼龍一開門就跑去都要排30分鐘，出嚟已經去到200分鐘<br />\n買咗express4 :<br />\nSpiderman wait time 90分鐘，排5分鐘左右<br />\n侏羅紀、大白鯊冇留意wait time，排5-10分鐘<br />\n禁忌之旅wait time200分鐘，直入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你好～我5月頭去撞正三日日本法定假期同weekend咁～你覺得係咪放weekdays 去會好d無咁多人？<br />\n另外會同小朋友去應該剩係陪佢玩兒童區有無fast pass買？ 我諗我應該無時間玩你介紹既機動遊戲了！<br />\nThx your 樓上詳盡介紹post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee2cfecd0946dc8c3f7170636bc67e8f8bb6739","tid":189172,"uid":58675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Recommend 買IC Card;我尋日大阪玩完翻黎，基本上好少用JR(因為佢d站好遠)，反而用電鐵同地下鐵多。同IC card既外國人ver.去某d sights會有discount,所以方便d。<br />\nUSJ記住買pass呀如果唔係一個遊戲要排100分鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIC卡同西瓜卡有無分別？<br />\n因為當年去東京買左西瓜卡<br />\n可否在大阪用？Thanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuica, pasmo, icoca等等, 統稱IC卡<br />\n大部分都已經共通</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx for reply!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2ea65bbe82aa81bc8e8c41ff544d2759366196","tid":189172,"uid":103946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來係咁，但你酒店個價貴唔貴？<br />\n同埋見巴打你編嘅行程，係唔係一支公去同埋自己本身中意睇名勝古蹟多於食野行街？</blockquote><br />\n係啊自己去<br />\n自己本身唔係好識食，食到好野都無咩感覺，所以費事特登搵餐廳，隨遇而安就算<br />\n名勝古蹟係一定要睇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n酒店就平均一晚$600港紙左右，應該唔算好貴<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你一個人去定同fd去呀?<br />\n我5月都去大阪wor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>14/5 - 18/5  一個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個人去啊，不過係8號果個禮拜，岩岩miss左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我住果間好正，500蚊左右晚，地點都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣可以介紹比您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook好左酒店啦，唔該晒絲打<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你可以上網計下交通費佑唔值回張pass，定一係買關西周遊pass抵。<br />\n<br />\n一張三日卡都係2000yen(好似係)，但pass成15000yen。話唔定周遊卡加額外車費平pass成倍。<br />\n<br />\n利申係關西租獨立屋，大部分都係用周遊卡<br />\n<br />\nIC卡唔抵，你搭一程都成幾百yen，如果用翻原價去玩關西肯定好貴<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n之前down左個「乘換案內」app，計過要大概10000yen左右，所以應該唔會買5日周遊券<br />\n我宜家打算學上面巴打話齋<br />\n買haruka連IC<br />\n跟住去姬路城果日用關西周遊券<br />\n(京都-&gt;姬路-&gt;大阪咁坐)<br />\n<br />\n京都果兩日就搭巴士／JR<br />\nBTW,原來關西周遊券同pass係兩樣野?"},{"pid":"d2b5370e572328cc1d6b002f39b88657a172c084","tid":189172,"uid":92806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來係咁，但你酒店個價貴唔貴？<br />\n同埋見巴打你編嘅行程，係唔係一支公去同埋自己本身中意睇名勝古蹟多於食野行街？</blockquote><br />\n係啊自己去<br />\n自己本身唔係好識食，食到好野都無咩感覺，所以費事特登搵餐廳，隨遇而安就算<br />\n名勝古蹟係一定要睇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n酒店就平均一晚$600港紙左右，應該唔算好貴<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你一個人去定同fd去呀?<br />\n我5月都去大阪wor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>14/5 - 18/5  一個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個人去啊，不過係8號果個禮拜，岩岩miss左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我住果間好正，500蚊左右晚，地點都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣可以介紹比您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook好左酒店啦，唔該晒絲打<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你可以上網計下交通費佑唔值回張pass，定一係買關西周遊pass抵。<br />\n<br />\n一張三日卡都係2000yen(好似係)，但pass成15000yen。話唔定周遊卡加額外車費平pass成倍。<br />\n<br />\n利申係關西租獨立屋，大部分都係用周遊卡<br />\n<br />\nIC卡唔抵，你搭一程都成幾百yen，如果用翻原價去玩關西肯定好貴<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n之前down左個「乘換案內」app，計過要大概10000yen左右，所以應該唔會買5日周遊券<br />\n我宜家打算學上面巴打話齋<br />\n買haruka連IC<br />\n跟住去姬路城果日用關西周遊券<br />\n(京都-&gt;姬路-&gt;大阪咁坐)<br />\n<br />\n京都果兩日就搭巴士／JR<br />\nBTW,原來關西周遊券同pass係兩樣野?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關西周遊劵係搭唔到JR架"},{"pid":"0f36b9c766c48421f676f5840c3aefb65867a9a1","tid":189172,"uid":7505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>14/5 - 18/5  一個人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我13-17/5一個人去wor<br />\n有興趣一齊傾既add我tg呀：kenyl1"},{"pid":"4c31e5cf80965dc3e77cc546560cbb664156157b","tid":189172,"uid":53041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n之前down左個「乘換案內」app，計過要大概10000yen左右，所以應該唔會買5日周遊券<br />\n我宜家打算學上面巴打話齋<br />\n買haruka連IC<br />\n跟住去姬路城果日用關西周遊券<br />\n(京都-&gt;姬路-&gt;大阪咁坐)<br />\n<br />\n京都果兩日就搭巴士／JR<br />\nBTW,原來關西周遊券同pass係兩樣野?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPass係統稱姐...<br />\n<br />\n京都-&gt;姬路-&gt;大阪<br />\n你應該買JR KANSAI area pass..下面條link果隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6f03780e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/pass/kansai/</a><br />\n<br />\n京都果兩日就可以買京都巴士一日卷..500羊任搭市內巴士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買pass前就自己計下值唔值"},{"pid":"18bd4b58cc3607f0e3a13d39b2351a655fb7e89b","tid":189172,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"巴打我都5月去大阪，留個名先<br />\n我住民宿，簡左個超讚屋主既屋，百幾個好評，呢啲應該幾有保證，而且又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab97a9442b1f87f845e808fd3e911600f82f8cbb","tid":189172,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"<